These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, sailing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, blues
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower
2 different games are played: bridge, canasta
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, grey
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person playing bridge##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who likes yellow##8
6. the thai is not the person who likes yellow##6
7. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | sailing   | cricket      |
| Music-Genre          | blues | indie   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Flower           | sunflower     | balloon-flower    |
| Game   | canasta    | bridge       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| Color     | yellow     | grey        |

